These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, time-travel, animation, adventure
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, train, subway
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the ship and the person driving the train##2
6. the person watching adventure movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | comedy     | animation | time-travel |
| Transport     | quad-bike     | train | subway  | ship      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, disco, indie, jazz
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, quad-bike
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
5. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | disco    | jazz     | indie  |
| Transport     | bike    | ship | car | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, classical, ambient, reggae
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, fish, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
2. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | classical   | ambient   | dubstep  | reggae |
| Pet           | hamster | mouse | fish | chinchilla  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, magic-tricks, baking, filmmaking
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, british, polish, nigerian
1. the nigerian is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is writing and the polish##2
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the polish is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | writing | filmmaking | baking  |
| Nationality   | british  | mexican   | nigerian  | polish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, camping, video-games, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | coffee   | cola | mirinda    |
| Hobby      | camping | dancing | video-games       | puzzles |

