.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, mirinda, hot-chocolate
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, subway, jet-ski, quad-bike
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person drinking mirinda##2
3. the person driving the car is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | 7up | mirinda | hot-chocolate | cola |
| Transport   | subway | car  | jet-ski    | quad-bike  |

