2. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the argentine is between the british and the brazilian##2
5. the person driving the car is the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the car is between the person driving the motorbike and the brazilian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | brazilian | argentine | british     |
| Transport     | boat | subway  | car   | motorbike |

