2. the person who's hobby is writing is the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
