.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, turtle, dog, goat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, cricket, weightlifting, snowboarding
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is golf##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | cat | turtle   | dog      | goat      |
| Sport   | cricket     | weightlifting | golf | snowboarding |

