.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, soul, hip-hop, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, british, thai, malaysian
1. the turkish is on the right of the british##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is between the malaysian and the british##2
3. the fan of soul is the british##1
4. the thai is on the left of the british##1
5. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the turkish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | soul | hip-hop      | punk   |
| Nationality   | thai  | british    | turkish | malaysian |

