.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, rock-climbing, collecting, dancing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, van, bus
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the bus is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
5. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
6. the person driving the van is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | skydiving | collecting | dancing    | rock-climbing      |
| Transport   | van       | bus       | helicopter | bike |

