.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, pakistani, polish, colombian
4 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, lizard, goat
1. the pakistani is on the far right##1
2. the indonesian is the indonesian##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
5. the polish is on the left or right of the colombian##3
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the colombian##3
7. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | polish  | colombian | pakistani |
| Pet           | lizard     | goat | horse    | guinea-pig     |

