.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, peach, cranberry, cucumber
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, teacher, accountant, electrician
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the teacher##3
2. the teacher is on the right of the accountant##1
3. the person eating peach is on the left of the videographer##1
4. the teacher is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | peach  | spinach | cucumber  | cranberry      |
| Job    | electrician | videographer | accountant | teacher |

