.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, skydiving, woodworking, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, blues, country, folk
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of blues is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
6. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku | woodworking | baking |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | r&b       | blues   | country      |

