5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | russian | egyptian | pakistani |
| Sport         | water-polo  | climbing   | tennis | sailing     |

