.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, mirinda, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, climbing, volleyball, parkour
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up     | iced-tea     | mirinda          | juice |
| Sport      | cricket | climbing | parkour | volleyball  |

 